12
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:05,960
Watch it.

13
00:01:06,120 --> 00:01:07,280
Wanna get fired?

14
00:01:08,360 --> 00:01:09,680
They're just after money.

15
00:01:10,120 --> 00:01:11,320
We are the ones suffering.

16
00:01:12,160 --> 00:01:13,080
That's right.

17
00:01:14,980 --> 00:01:18,140
(Horse)

18
00:01:27,720 --> 00:01:28,560
I'm back.

19
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:34,960
The time has come.

20
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:36,200
We can make our move.

21
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:43,680
Zhang Wangfu is eyeing a parcel in Jiangbei.

22
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:44,960
But,

23
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:46,240
