24
00:01:46,800 --> 00:01:48,320
I invested through an overseas trust

25
00:01:48,360 --> 00:01:49,320
in several

26
00:01:49,320 --> 00:01:50,800
real estate firms in Kanglan.

27
00:01:51,240 --> 00:01:53,160
They've all become his rivals.

28
00:01:53,480 --> 00:01:54,760
I have a concern now.

29
00:01:54,880 --> 00:01:55,720
Go ahead.

30
00:01:56,180 --> 00:01:58,320
Zhang Wangfu lacks funds now,

31
00:01:58,760 --> 00:01:59,600
however,

32
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:01,320
real estate is just part of his business,

33
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:02,840
and it won't crush him.

34
00:02:03,160 --> 00:02:04,000
Right.

35
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:05,160
That's why

36
00:02:05,240 --> 00:02:06,920
we must corner him completely.

37
00:02:07,600 --> 00:02:08,480
Also,

38
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:10,080
we need to find more strategies

39
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:11,120
in other fields.

40
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:12,480
The key is

41
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:14,680
to keep him busy.

42
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:17,240
Do you have any ideas?

43
00:02:25,720 --> 00:02:26,560
Sir,

44
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:28,720
someone sold the shares this morning.

45
00:02:28,920 --> 00:02:30,400
The stock price is dropping sharply.

46
00:02:30,410 --> 00:02:31,280
What?

47
00:02:34,880 --> 00:02:35,880
Keep buying for me.

48
00:02:36,140 --> 00:02:37,030
Alright.

49
00:02:37,040 --> 00:02:38,560
I put it all in there.

50
00:02:38,760 --> 00:02:39,920
Don't mess it up.

51
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:41,200
I won't, Ms. Hong.

52
00:02:41,440 --> 00:02:43,320
Sir, the bank approved the loan.

53
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:46,880
Great. Now let's see who dares to compete.

54
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:48,800
We got a situation.

55
00:02:48,810 --> 00:02:49,670
What is it?

56
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:50,680
Word has it

57
00:02:50,880 --> 00:02:52,880
Lucheng Construction increased their bid.

58
00:02:53,080 --> 00:02:53,960
Again?

59
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,120
We'll raise it, too.

60
00:02:55,320 --> 00:02:56,880
Raise it!

61
00:02:57,040 --> 00:02:58,400
Sir.

62
00:02:58,760 --> 00:02:59,680
What?

63
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,480
We bid on several projects but failed.

64
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,400
How's that possible?

65
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,520
Sir, thank you.

66
00:03:04,790 --> 00:03:05,670
No need.

67
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:07,800
Your proposal scored the highest.

68
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:08,960
It's well-deserved.

69
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:10,600
Looking forward to our cooperation.

70
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:12,400
Take care.

71
00:03:12,760 --> 00:03:13,600
See you.

72
00:03:16,880 --> 00:03:17,720
Okay, then.

73
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:19,800
Thanks for your help.

74
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:22,400
Sure.

75
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:23,680
Goodbye.

76
00:03:25,440 --> 00:03:26,800
Good for you, Legal Boy.

77
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:28,360
This is just the beginning.

78
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:30,120
We're just getting started.

79
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:32,360
Did you get it?

80
00:03:33,350 --> 00:03:34,240
How much did you get it for?

81
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:36,440
Three hundred?

82
00:03:36,760 --> 00:03:37,600
Three times.

83
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:39,000
Triple the price?

84
00:03:39,320 --> 00:03:40,960
That's insane.

85
00:03:41,170 --> 00:03:43,200
Sir, you said whatever it takes…

86
00:03:43,200 --> 00:03:44,320
Forget it.

87
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:46,840
As long as we get that parcel,

88
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:49,400
we can secure the foreign investment.

89
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:51,280
Our cash flow barely covers next month.

90
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:53,400
Sell the properties in the south.

91
00:03:53,500 --> 00:03:55,640
Someone from the south site is looking for you.

92
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:56,680
Who is it?

93
00:04:03,200 --> 00:04:05,080
Uncle Wangfu, long time no see.

94
00:04:05,760 --> 00:04:06,840
Legal Boy?

95
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:08,000
What brings you here?

96
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,560
I'm working in the south.

97
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:10,520
I heard

98
00:04:11,150 --> 00:04:12,600
