100
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:17,400
What do you mean?

101
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:18,560
Nothing much.

102
00:04:19,070 --> 00:04:21,600
The site used inferior materials,

103
00:04:21,950 --> 00:04:22,960
and I reported it.

104
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:25,160
Thanks for the gifts, everyone.

105
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:26,320
Thank you all.

106
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:29,640
By the way, here's a news update.

107
00:04:29,960 --> 00:04:31,080
I'd like to report

108
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:33,680
Dongcan Group is using substandard cement,

109
00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:35,840
