113
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,480
hitting an all-time low.

114
00:05:01,840 --> 00:05:03,080
Why panic?

115
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:08,520
Do they think it can defeat me?

116
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:12,400
Naive. Truly naive.

117
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:18,320
Don't you trust me?

118
00:05:19,200 --> 00:05:21,720
Through all these years with Dongcan Group,

119
00:05:21,880 --> 00:05:23,720
haven't I solved every problem?

120
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:29,400
As long as the overseas Corona Investments

121
00:05:29,960 --> 00:05:31,320
can fulfill the contract on time.

122
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:32,840
Our Dongcan

123
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:35,280
will resolve the crisis.

124
00:05:43,740 --> 00:05:44,640
I am

125
00:05:45,840 --> 00:05:47,600
still top-notch in the city.

126
00:05:54,840 --> 00:05:56,041
We've reached the final agreement

127
00:05:56,057 --> 00:05:57,840
with America's Corona Investments.

128
00:05:58,560 --> 00:05:59,920
That's great.

129
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:01,680
Once they come in,

130
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:03,280
things will be easier for us.

131
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,840
Check again carefully.

132
00:06:11,640 --> 00:06:13,760
See if there are any materials

133
00:06:15,210 --> 00:06:16,280
that haven't been retrieved.

134
00:06:16,280 --> 00:06:17,140
Mm.

135
00:06:17,150 --> 00:06:18,370
All clear.

136
00:06:30,520 --> 00:06:31,360
Chongguang?

137
00:06:36,520 --> 00:06:38,200
Chongguang, why are you back?

138
00:06:41,470 --> 00:06:42,320
Uncle Wangfu.

139
00:06:42,900 --> 00:06:43,880
Long time no see.

140
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:47,000
Long time no see.

141
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:49,760
Well,

142
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:51,380
what brings you

143
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,640
here today?

144
00:06:54,840 --> 00:06:57,360
I am the China Regional Director
of Corona Group,

145
00:06:57,880 --> 00:06:58,720
Zhang Chongguang.

146
00:07:00,760 --> 00:07:02,120
You can't give up on yourself

147
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:04,280
