153
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:16,400
Dad,

154
00:07:17,640 --> 00:07:18,640
I'll be back.

155
00:07:25,200 --> 00:07:26,360
Corona Group?

156
00:07:28,080 --> 00:07:28,920
